  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The expression above can be written in the form <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, times y squared, plus b\"></span></span>, where <span class=\"italic\">a</span> and <span class=\"italic\">b</span> are constants. What is the value of <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, plus b\"></span></span> ?</p>\n",
