  "rationale": "<p>The correct answer is 6632. Applying the distributive property to the expression yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, 7532 plus 100 y squared, close parenthesis, plus, open parenthesis, 100 y squared, minus 1100, close parenthesis\"></span>. Then adding together <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"7532 plus 100 y squared\"></span> and <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"100 y squared, minus 1100\"></span> and collecting like terms results in <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"200 y squared, plus 6432\"></span>. This is written in the form <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, y squared, plus b\"></span>, where <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, equals 200 \"></span> and <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"b equals 6432\"></span>. Therefore <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, plus b equals, 200 plus 6432, which equals 6632\"></span>.</p>\n",
